edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model

Interface Annotation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FormattableObject, WapObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RdfAnnotation

    public interface Annotation
extends WapObject
    The annotation interface contains all methods special to annotations. As most of the needed functionality is already defined in WapObject there are only a few addressing the container IRI and the question if a target exists.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matthias Dressel, Michael Hitzker, Markus Hoefler, Andreas Loeffler, Timo Schmidt
